        <briefdescription>
<para>The MUX Controller constructor. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para><hruler/>
</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>mux_gpios</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Array with gpio information for muxer select lines </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>num_mux</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The number of muxer select lines </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>enable_gpio</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Structure with gpio information for muxer enable pin</para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
The function initializes the GPIO pins of the muxer select lines with array mux_gpios of type struct gpio_dt_spec, the number of muxer select lines with parameter num_mux and mux enable pin with structure enable_gpio of type struct gpio_dt_spec. </para>
        </detaileddescription>
        <inbodydescription>
        </inbodydescription>
