    <briefdescription>
<para>MUX Controller driver class. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><hruler/>
</para>
<para><simplesect kind="par"><title>Detailed Description </title><para>The MUX Controller driver class handle the selection of the connected analog inputs and connect the selcted channel to the drain pin, which acts as output and is connected to the analog input pin 14 / AIN1 of the NRF9160. The class provides methods to select the analog input channel, to enable or disable the analog input, to print the status and to retrieve the nuimber of attached analog input signals. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
